data.name: Label1.Text
data.value:
This project is a continuation of an earlier effort begun in 2005 by Jeff Nickel, aka Phishbwlr. His vision was a restoration of the Prodigy® Chat community with a free-to-use chat application based on IRC, but retaining the look and feel of the old Prodigy® Chat service.
For various reasons, this early version of the program fizzled out in 2009. Due to a resurgence in interest, however, the project was revisited in August 2014. This new version of the program has been written completely from scratch, including the development of a proprietary chat server in the place of IRC. The Prodigy Restoration Team has put hundreds of hours of hard work in to this application, so that we might provide Prodigy® community members with the most authentic experience possible.
It is with great pride that we present ProdStar Communicate to you, and we sincerely hope you enjoy its use as much as we enjoyed its development.
